Package: bridgesampling
Type: Package
Title: Bridge Sampling for Obtaining Marginal Likelihoods
Version: 0.1-0
Authors@R: c(person(given="Quentin F.", family="Gronau", role=c("aut", "cre"),
             email="Quentin.F.Gronau@gmail.com"), person(given="Henrik",
             family="Singmann", role="aut"))
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: mvtnorm, Matrix, Brobdingnag, stringr, coda, parallel
Suggests: testthat, Rcpp
Description: Provides functions for estimating marginal likelihoods, Bayes factors,
             posterior model probabilities, and normalizing constants in general,
             via different versions of bridge sampling (see Meng & Wong, 1996).
